front.title: Incom T-16 Skyhopper
front.gametext: May add 1 passenger. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. May move as a 'react.' * Landspeed = 4. OR 1 character may shuttle to or from same site for free.
front.lore: Enclosed vehicle used for shuttling and hot-rodding. E-16/x ion engine pushes T-16 up to 1200 kph.
